'''潛龍屬'''（[[學名|屬名]]：{{lang|la|''Hyphalosaurus''}}，意為「潛隱水下的蜥蜴」），一名'''中國水生蜥'''<ref name = "Smith2001">{{cite journal | author = Smith, J. B., Harris, J. D. | title = A Taxonomic problem concerning two diapsid genera from the Lower Yixian Formation of Liaoning Province, Northeastern China | journal = ''Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology'' | volume = 21 | issue = 2 | year = 2001 | pages = 389-391 | issn = 0272-4634 | doi = 10.1671/0272-4634(2001)021[0389:ATPCTD]2.0.CO;2 | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/232672400_A_Taxonomic_problem_concerning_two_diapsid_genera_from_the_Lower_Yixian_Formation_of_Liaoning_Province_Northeastern_China }}</ref><ref name = "Ji2014">{{cite journal | author = 季燕南、王旭日、季强 | title = 中国水生蜥与潜龙名称合法性之争 | journal = 地质学刊 | volume = 38 | issue = 1 | year = 2014 | pages = 12-16 | issn = 1674-3636 | doi = 10.3969/j.issn.1674-3636.2014.01.12 | url =  }}</ref>，是生存於[[早白堊世|早白堊世]]的[[水生動物|水生]][[爬行動物|爬行動物]]<ref name = "Gao1999">{{cite journal | author = 高克勤、唐治路、汪筱林 | title = 辽宁晚侏罗世~早白垩世一长颈双弓类爬行动物 | journal = 古脊椎动物学报 | volume = 37 | issue = 1 | year = 1999 | pages = 1-8 | issn = 1000-3118 | doi = 10.19615/j.cnki.1000-3118.1999.01.001 | url = http://www.ivpp.cas.cn/cbw/gjzdwxb/xbwzxz/200812/W020090813369479639247.pdf | access-date = 2020-01-31 | archive-date = 2020-05-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200517142952/http://www.ivpp.cas.cn/cbw/gjzdwxb/xbwzxz/200812/W020090813369479639247.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>，屬於[[離龍目|離龍目]][[潛龍科|潛龍科]]，身形纖長，為[[熱河生物群|熱河生物群]]的代表性生物之一。本屬已知的化石至少有數千具，包含其[[生活史|生活史]]各個階段，從[[胚胎|胚胎]]到完全成年的個體皆有。這些化石皆發現自[[中國|中國]][[遼寧省|遼寧省]]西部，其中絕大部分都是由[[熱河群|熱河群]]的[[義縣組|義縣組]]地層出土，因而成為該地層化石發現數量最多的[[四足動物|四足動物]]<ref name = "Gao2008">{{cite journal | author = Gao, K.-Q.; Ksepka, D. T. | title = Osteology and taxonomic revision of ''Hyphalosaurus'' (Diapsida: Choristodera) from the Lower Cretaceous of Liaoning, China | journal = ''Journal of Anatomy'' | volume = 212 | issue = 6 | year = 2008 | pages = 747-768 | issn = 0021-8782 | doi = 10.1111/j.1469-7580.2008.00907.x | url = https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2423398/ | pmc = 2423398 | pmid = 18510504 }}</ref>。

潛龍屬共有兩個[[物種|物種]]，即[[模式種|模式種]]'''凌源潛龍'''（''H. lingyuanensis''），以及頸部較長的'''白台溝潛龍'''（''H. baitaigouensis''），兩物種有紀錄的成體全長皆可超過80公分，其中白台溝潛龍最大個體的全長更可達110公分，為中大型的離龍類，體型可能略大於同科的[[莊川龍|莊川龍]]<ref name = "Gao2008"/><ref name = "Matsumoto2010">{{cite journal | author = Matsumoto, R., Evans, S. E. | title = Choristoderes and the freshwater assemblages of Laurasia | journal = ''Journal of Iberian Geology'' | volume = 36 | issue = 2 | year = 2010 | pages = 253-274 | issn = 1886-7995 | doi = 10.5209/rev_JIGE.2010.v36.n2.11 | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/228117662_Choristoderes_and_the_freshwater_assemblages_of_Laurasia | access-date = 2020-01-31 | archive-date = 2021-07-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210719133703/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/228117662_Choristoderes_and_the_freshwater_assemblages_of_Laurasia | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

然而，[[正模標本|正模標本]]所處的兩個岩塊分給兩群不同的科學家。兩群科學家各自敘述，並公佈研究結果，讓這群動物有兩個不同名字：潛龍（''Hyphalosaurus''）、中國水生蜥（''Sinohydrosaurus''）。後來兩者被承認是來自同一標本，因為潛龍較早命名具有優先權，所以中國水生蜥被認為是潛龍的[[次異名|次異名]]。

從延長的頸部與縮短的四肢外形，可確定潛龍為水生爬行動物。潛龍的外表類似小型[[幻龍類|幻龍類]]，幻龍類是在[[三疊紀|三疊紀]]滅絕的[[海生爬行動物|海生爬行動物]]。這些類似處是驅同演化的結果，並不表示牠們有演化上的關係。

潛龍屬於[[離龍目|離龍目]]，與大型、類似[[鱷魚|鱷魚]]的[[鱷龍|鱷龍]]，以及小型、類似[[蜥蜴|蜥蜴]]的[[滿洲鱷|滿洲鱷]]有接近親緣關係。[[離龍目|離龍目]]在[[白堊紀末滅絕事件|白堊紀末滅絕事件]]中存活下來，而在[[中新世|中新世]]滅絕。

在2007年，挖掘到一個1億2000萬年前的雙頭潛龍化石，這是目前有紀錄的最古老[[雙頭動物|雙頭動物]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,244603,00.html?sPage=fnc.science/evolution|title=Prehistoric Reptile Fossil Found With Two Heads|last=Than|first=Ker|date=2007-01-18|newspaper=Fox News|accessdate=2018-07-13|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101031135438/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,244603,00.html?sPage=fnc.science%2Fevolution|archive-date=2010-10-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/6195345.stm|title=Two-headed reptile fossil found|date=2006-12-20|accessdate=2018-07-13|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126202507/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/6195345.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Buffetaut et al. (2006) "A two-headed reptile from the Cretaceous of China" Biology Letters [http://journals.royalsociety.org/content/08427xp462431367/fulltext.html Early Online] {{Wayback|url=http://journals.royalsociety.org/content/08427xp462431367/fulltext.html |date=20180713143239 }} (DOI: 10.1098/rsbl.2006.0580)</ref>。

